{"tid":1360591,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"睇tvb大嘅藍絲老母 有個警察姐夫 都開始變黃","createTime":"2019-07-24T11:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T17:12:25.000Z","uid":23229,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e8e2069ece40948ab6433990d021982b22c70c56","tid":1360591,"uid":23229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:24:20.000Z","msg":"話說今日我著黑衫出街<br />\n我老母問我係咪唔驚比人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話唔會打到我嘅<br />\n佢話元朗啲人好痴線 叫我小心啲<br />\n佢仲講得出何妖鬧朱凱迪<br />\n我好開心佢竟然有留意<br />\n<br />\n原本嘅佢仲講緊話叫我唔好去遊行<br />\n話淋病已經讓左步<br />\n宜家佢變左叫我小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我姨媽仲share緊啲on9 post話係黑衫換白衫打人<br />\n日日就話撐警 話警察保護香港 香港先有和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢老公係退休警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個情況下我媽仲無比佢薰陶到變深藍<br />\n我已經好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知你地啲屋企人又有無改變呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8669ed393a61a24e87784df880caf81473f024","tid":1360591,"uid":23229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T11:29:13.000Z","msg":"平時成日同老母鬧交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日真係有啲感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba99d9e97bcca1cbaa6fbd625ed062728e730053","tid":1360591,"uid":19725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bf8669ed393a61a24e87784df880caf81473f024","tid":1360591,"uid":23229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"